sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as api.orders
    participant Connect as tradex.connect
    participant OMS_A as EphemeralOMS
    participant Broker
    participant Bus as EventBus
    participant OMS_B as DI_TradingContext
    participant PM as PositionManager

    Note over Client,PM: CURRENT BROKEN PATH
    Client->>API: POST /orders
    API->>Connect: connect per request
    Connect->>OMS_A: new OrderManager unsubscribed
    OMS_A->>Broker: place order
    Broker-->>Bus: TRADE event
    Bus->>OMS_B: on_trade different instance
    API->>Connect: session.close destroys OMS_A
    Client->>API: GET /orders
    API->>OMS_B: get_order stale ack status

    Note over Client,PM: TARGET PATH
    Client->>API: POST /orders
    API->>OMS_B: place_order singleton
    OMS_B->>Broker: place via transport
    Broker-->>Bus: TRADE
    Bus->>OMS_B: on_trade same instance
    Bus->>PM: TRADE_APPLIED update position
    Client->>API: GET /orders
    API->>OMS_B: get_order reflects fill
